{"tid":9654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不港獨下爭民主？重溫831","createTime":"2016-11-28T16:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T19:11:41.000Z","uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cd8b72d509e8dd7261b05faa63557d633a682c","tid":9654,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"人大常委會於2014年8月31日作出了三項決定：<br />\n(1) 2017年有權提名特首候選人的，只有提名委員會，而人數、組成和委員的產生辦法，依舊按照現行由1200人，四大界別組成的選舉委員會產生辦法。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 特首參選人須取得過半數提委會委員提名，才能出閘選特首。<br />\n<br />\n(3) 限制提名委員會只能選出2至3個候選人。<br />\n<br />\n連改革提名委員會都ban撚左，肥彭重講乜鳩點解冇人講過令提名委員會更民主呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陳方安生甚至陳宏偽個方案都唔乎合831呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387f610a89f33441cac0d694aca236f15a64b806","tid":9654,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"不脫離中共<br />\n民主必然假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4db0a815c90a7824f02f3cc8285a4e6ffce2b3","tid":9654,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不脫離中共<br />\n民主必然假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家係諗點樣令港獨可以有更多人支持"},{"pid":"67c1dedca5790de834a714d152ce9f4821b9e01d","tid":9654,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班好似2014年冇發生過咁，點解港獨會爆出黎又唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001097f59d207d51502d03d769d33b16fe92e686","tid":9654,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237e992bad49f8934934421051b275dc95510959","tid":9654,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":